flyer1.Explanation: Inu {999}} dun lati kede ifilọlẹ oju opo wẹẹbu wa tuntun. O pẹlu atokọ dagba ti awọn ẹya, gẹgẹbi:
flyer1.Private: A ikọkọ olumulo iroyin fun gbogbo omo egbe
flyer1.Notifications: Nipa titẹ adirẹsi imeeli rẹ tabi nọmba alagbeka iwọ yoo ni anfani lati gba awọn iwifunni pataki nipasẹ imeeli tabi ifọrọranṣẹ.
flyer1.GetStarted: Lati bẹrẹ, ninu ẹrọ aṣawakiri wẹẹbu rẹ jọwọ farabalẹ tẹ sii:
flyer1.IssuedToYou: Koodu yii jẹ pataki fun ọ.
